imed catastrophic mass loss by continuing to accrete dense gas\ncondensing from a gravitationally-confined ionized phase.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Sep 2017 23:18:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Nov 2017 14:10:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-05-23"}
